Ustad Mobile iOS builder
17/Dec/2013 - Last updated by Varuna Singh

Before you build: Pre-Requisites:

Have Xcode
Have iPhone SDK installed 
(Typically post Mac OSX.7)
Have cordova and npm

run this before building and emulating.

sudo npm install -g ios-sim
The above command will make sure the project can be simulated (emulated) in the iOS simulator.

Have fun!


To build:

./setup-ios.sh 

To run on connected device (must have USB debugging enabled):

./setup-ios.sh run

To run emulator:

./setup-ios.sh emulate

